- âœ… Media file (MP3, MP4, or both)
- âœ… Full metadata (.info.json)
- âœ… Video description
- âœ… Transcripts/subtitles (if available)
- âœ… Thumbnail image
- âœ… Live chat (if available)

**All automatically organized in one folder!**

